 <body> 
  <p>The rating component, a <a href="../../communities/using/tally.md">tally</a> subclass, allows signed in community members to rate a feature on the website.</p> 
  <p>Placing multiple instances of a voting component on the same page is allowed; each instance must be configured with an unique <span class="code">tally name</span> property.</p> 
  <p>Anonymous posting of a rating is not supported. Site visitors must register and sign in to participate in a rating only once. The signed in visitor (member) may change their rating at any time.</p> 
